BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTAMP:20170606T232312Z
UID:0ody6uvHl2-8232010117@spjnetwork.org
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260409
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260409
SUMMARY:Nomination Deadline: Julie Galvan Outstanding Graduate in Journalism Award
URL:http://www.spj.org/julie-galvan-outstanding-graduate-in-journalism-award/
DESCRIPTION:Each of the Society’s campus chapters are encouraged to select one graduate in journalism who is outstanding in his or her class on the basis of character\, service to the community\, scholarship\, proficiency in practical journalism and significant contributions to their SPJ chapter. From this group\, the Society’s leaders will select one graduate who is considered the most outstanding for national recognition.

The Award is named in memory of Julie Galvan\, a former president of the SPJ San Jose State University Campus Chapter.
LOCATION:
END:VEVENT





BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTAMP:20170606T232313Z
UID:y2d7X07e4J-8232091219@spjnetwork.org
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260410
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260410
SUMMARY:‘It's a Dry Beat: Speaking Truth in a Truthiness Age,’ SPJ 2026 Region 11 Conference
URL:http://phoenixspj.org
DESCRIPTION:Learn\, network and get your questions answered about challenges facing journalists in 2026 with colleagues from Arizona\, California\, Hawaii\, Nevada and the Pacific Islands at an affordable one-day conference packed with relevance! It's Friday\, April 10\, at the fabulous Flinn Foundation building in central Phoenix. We'll also present the Region 11 Mark of Excellence Awards to student journalists. Details and registration will be available starting in January at phoenixspj.org.
LOCATION:1802 North Central Avenue\, Phoenix\, AZ\, USA
END:VEVENT





BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTAMP:20170606T232314Z
UID:DoVfyk1x60-8229088469@spjnetwork.org
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260413
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260415
SUMMARY:International Conference on Public Health and Health Care System
URL:http:// publichealth.pagesconferences.org/
DESCRIPTION:PAGES conferences are excited to invite you to the upcoming International Conference on Public Health and Health Care System\, scheduled to take place from April 13-15\, 2026 in the city of finance Paris\, France. 

This event will bring together leading experts for keynote addresses\, dynamic panel discussions\, and engaging workshops that aim to poster collaboration and inspire innovative ideas. Topics will span a range of critical areas\, including disease prevention\, health promotion\, epidemiology\, environmental health\, and global health policy.

Overall\, the  International Conference on Public Health and Health Care Research and Development promises to be an important forum for advancing our understanding of Public Health and Health Care and exploring innovative solutions to global health challenges. 

We eagerly anticipate your participation in this exciting and inspiring event in Paris\, France.
LOCATION:Paris\, France
END:VEVENT





BEGIN:VEVENT
